# Spring Boot — Test Patterns

## Stack context
- Java 11, Spring Boot 2.x → dùng `javax.validation` (KHÔNG phải `jakarta`)
- JUnit 5 + Mockito (`@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class)`)
- Build tool: Maven (`mvn test`, `mvn verify`)

## Chọn đúng test slice

| Cần test gì | Annotation | Load gì |
|---|---|---|
| Controller (HTTP layer) | `@WebMvcTest(XController.class)` | Chỉ web layer, mock service |
| JPA repository + MySQL | `@DataJpaTest` | JPA + H2 in-memory |
| MongoDB repository | `@DataMongoTest` | Embedded MongoDB |
| Kafka consumer/listener | `@SpringBootTest` + `@EmbeddedKafka` | Full context + embedded broker |
| Pure business logic | Không annotation, plain JUnit 5 | Không load Spring |
| Full integration | `@SpringBootTest(webEnvironment=RANDOM_PORT)` | Toàn bộ context |

## Unit test (service/usecase)
```java
@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class)
class LmsAccountServiceTest {
    @Mock LmsAccountsRepository repo;
    @InjectMocks LmsAccountServiceImpl service;

    @Test
    void should_returnAccount_when_usernameExists() { ... }
}
```

## Controller test
```java
@WebMvcTest(AuthController.class)
class AuthControllerTest {
    @Autowired MockMvc mockMvc;
    @MockBean AuthService authService;

    @Test
    void should_return401_when_passwordWrong() throws Exception {
        mockMvc.perform(post("/api/auth/login").content(...))
               .andExpect(status().isUnauthorized());
    }
}
```

## JPA repository test
```java
@DataJpaTest
class LmsAccountsRepositoryTest {
    @Autowired LmsAccountsRepository repo;
    // H2 auto-configured, rollback sau mỗi test
}
```

## Kafka consumer test
```java
@SpringBootTest
@EmbeddedKafka(partitions = 1, topics = {"club-game-result"})
class GameResultListenerTest {
    @Autowired KafkaTemplate<String, String> template;
    // Gửi message → assert side effect
}
```

## Test naming convention
```
should_{expected_behavior}_when_{condition}
```
Ví dụ: `should_throwRunException_when_accountNotFound`

## Mock chỉ ở boundary
- Mock: Repository, Kafka producer, Redis, external HTTP client
- KHÔNG mock: Service gọi Service khác nội bộ (dùng integration test thay)

## RunException pattern
```java
assertThrows(RunException.class, () -> service.login("wrong", "pass"));
```

## Multi-module Maven
Chạy test 1 module: `mvn test -pl lms-api -am`
Chạy toàn bộ: `mvn verify`
